【Aromatherapy Diffusers with Remote Control】500ml large capacity ultrasonic fragrance diffuser machine works for up to 8 to 12 hours.The ultrasonic aromatherapy diffuser included 3 timer setting modes: 60min / 120min / 180min / ON.This large room diffuser for essential oils with remote control to easily set the working mode of the aroma humidifier while you sleep.
【7 Colors Changing LED Light】This electric aroma diffuser has 7 colors LED light. Press the "Light" button to adjust any color you like (monochrome/continuous color switch). It can also be a night light for sleep to adjust your sleeping atmosphere.
【Multifunctional Aroma Oil Mister】The cool mist aroma diffuser can also be worked as a Humidifier / Aroma Machine / Night Light. This ultrasonic diffuser and add essential oils as an aromatherapy machine to experience aromatherapy also humidifier to dry air,create a comfortable living space.
【BPA-Free & Auto Shut-Off】This aroma diffuser is made of high-quality BPA-free materials, which generate heat during use and will not affect the surrounding environment. Likewise, it will not harm you or your family. This essential oil vaporizer is equipped with an automatic shutdown function, when the water runs out or the time is up, it will automatically shut down, ensuring the safety of use when no one is there.
【Adjustable Timer & Mist Mode】This water diffuser comes with 3 freely adjustable timers: 60min / 120min / 180min and continuous diffusion. You can adjust it via the "MIST" button on the diffuser. This cool mist diffuser has 2 switchable mist modes: continuousntermittent. It is also adjusted through the "MIST" button, which is very convenient.
